to read the whole string us sc.nextLine() instead of sc.next()
String str=sc.nextLine();
System.out.println(str);
this prints the whole string
like: input is 
my name is kush oza
output with above: my name is kush oza


but if i had used sc.next()
ex: String str1;
str1=sc.next();
input: my name is kush oza
output: my 


so with string datatype use sc.nextLine();
